# Fresh Market 🛒

An E-commerce web application built with Angular.

## 🚀 Features
- User Authentication (Login / Register)
- Route Guards Protection
- Product Listing & Details
- Cart & Wishlist
- Online & Cash Payment Flow
- Responsive Design

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- Angular
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- RxJS
- ngx-toastr
- ngx-spinner

## 📦 Installation
```bash
npm install
ng serve
